query:
SELECT g.id as gestor_id, u.name 
FROM gestores g 
JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id 
WHERE u.name IN ('Fabio Dias', 'Marco Vilar', 'Carlos Eduardo', 'Marco Amorim')
ORDER BY u.name;
